Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:38.78,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}去实现于天空彼方的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:46.41,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我祈愿与你并肩前行
Comment: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:48.52,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:53.22,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正确与否
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:55.57,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只取决于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:23:03.44,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}时而莫衷一是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:10.35,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}时而词不达意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:12.41,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}这也无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:15.87,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}让弱小的我变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:21.42,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}是为与你相称
Comment: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:25.90,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I ain’t fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:27.90,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我难以割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:32.39,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}亦如无法放弃
